# Heading Indices

Use numbered sections following this pattern:

```markdown
- Main Topic
  - 01 First Section
  - 02 Second Section
    - 02.00 General Content
    - 02.01 First Subsection
    - 02.02 Second Subsection
    - 02.03 Third Subsection
      - 02.03.a First Detail
      - 02.03.b Second Detail
```

Rules:
1. Only leaf headers should contain content
2. For parent section content, use a ".00" subsection (e.g., "02.00 General Content")
3. Maximum heading depth: 3 levels
